@node "MAIN" "Welcome"
                                  @{b}@{u}TASC v2.3@{ub}@{uu}


These are going to be brief notes on the installation & use of Thor Auto Spam
Complainer.thor (TASC).


It's not really complete yet and almost completely based on TASC v1.8 doc


     @{" Requirements " link "Needs" 0}

     @{" Installation " link "Install" 0}

     @{" Configuration " link "Config" 0}

     @{" Usage " link "Use" 0}   @{" How it works? " link "WHAT" 0}

